{"tid":1844582,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"醫護小型罷工 政府即跪 吠都唔敢吠 香港人仲唔即刻行動？","createTime":"2020-01-26T16:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T17:44:48.000Z","uid":51039,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e9c100636d08a96c5dbf2d92c038057d5ccc1607","tid":1844582,"uid":51039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:44:39.000Z","msg":"見到罷工效果未？<br />\n以前日日話罷，又依樣唔得，又果樣唔掂<br />\n今獲有曬理由，唔洗和你塞，唔洗搞乜大型預先召集<br />\n有曬理由，一句感冒唔舒服有小小咳搞撚掂<br />\n有包伏咪翻一日工，咳翻幾聲<br />\n你老細叫你快d翻屋企咪留係到獻世<br />\n<br />\n逼封關順手逼埋五大訴求，獨立委員會，反擊黑警<br />\n共產黨忙個瘟疫都冇時間好似之前咁同你玩咁多動作<br />\n再配合貿易戰part2 內外夾擊，收佢皮<br />\n<br />\n講驚死，藍絲仲驚過你<br />\n論自私，同支那人同級<br />\n唔封關，藍絲屌曬老母<br />\n今日粉嶺仲黃藍曾經一齊做野<br />\n港共處事黃藍都屌，近日黑警行為一樣黃藍都屌<br />\n黑警仲保護同推薦大陸人嚟香港醫病<br />\n<br />\n對家港共同警犬到依㗎都咁撚on9<br />\n我地成日話人地蠢，依㗎有曬天時地利人和<br />\n又搞唔搞得出咩見得人嘅行動？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即刻大三罷，可以有計劃一齊<br />\n但都可以無需計劃，自己評定<br />\n雙重配合，罷工就會成自然</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天賜良機，唔用正on9"},{"pid":"d372c1eb7191fb87080711e94dc83648bd1c1706","tid":1844582,"uid":51039,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:49:29.000Z","msg":"自己話唔舒服又好<br />\n驚感染又好<br />\n依個時勢大把攞正牌嘅理由<br />\n有包袱？<br />\n肺炎死左仲有冇包袱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715420192e9bc35d521695e850805f478172e679","tid":1844582,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943f17b1d1b1807d144defcf19dd1a71c7240fcb","tid":1844582,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:57:13.000Z","msg":"【武漢x香港】手足聯動，五大訴求，延燒大陸！ 就蔥友和香港手足聯合發起文宣戰倡議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844488</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f6806d544210ac0d59798c5961d0b34a638f92d","tid":1844582,"uid":51039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"香港係一流城市<br />\n件件支那人都仆住落嚟醫<br />\n到時醫院冇曬位<br />\n香港人可能連死係醫院走廊嘅位都冇<br />\n<br />\n翻工？份工重要過你條命我咪收皮囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6cf9a32ec50f17d0c411d3714a450f30086315","tid":1844582,"uid":51039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:00:09.000Z","msg":"叫五大訴求叫大半年<br />\n人人話有包袱<br />\n大部野推落勇武身上，叫佢地做<br />\n依㗎真係影響自己條命，掉得低未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fe39140062304d2093fb693259384bb8f45066","tid":1844582,"uid":51039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:05:38.000Z","msg":"有邊個抗爭地方好似香港咁有福氣<br />\n每準備被淡化收皮，準備被逼做二等公民<br />\n對家就會嚟料激發翻民怨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依㗎仲有天幫，準備天滅中共<br />\n直接幫手打最終boss<br />\n我地配合收成<br />\n做唔做到？咁就要睇香港人自己喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719c5287290507e87c4cce8596fe24888baf2ba2","tid":1844582,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T17:05:59.000Z","msg":"Objective:<br />\n&gt; Shut down the airline from HK, if Carrie Lam fails to block the border.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSolomon都有講話禁止中國航班飛美國，不過要請佢留意埋香港：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropG58GJy%2FOqJThD